title: Meta House Art Cafe
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Western, Beer/Wine, European, Cambodian, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. The restaurant and bar of the Meta House, a cultural centre known for its film and documentary screenings, art exhibits, and is a meeting hub for those interested in the arts. Offers a variety of cuisines from western style food and snacks to German and Cambodian cuisine. Specialties are the German flamecakes, black bread, pumpkin gnocchi in tomato-sage sauce. Vegetarian items are marked with a green V (ovo, lacto).
